      propertyPath: dialogueStages.Array.data[0].lines.Array.size
      value: 6
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueStages.Array.data[1].lines.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueStages.Array.data[2].lines.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueStages.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: HI what are you doing here?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueStages.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: 'Oh, Your looking for the Air Crystal. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueStages.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: Its on the abandoned temple island
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueStages.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[3]'
      value: I would Let you use my airship, but The recent storm has blown away
        parts of my airship away
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueStages.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[4]'
      value: The propellor, Rudder and Energy Crystal have been blown away to the
        islands behind me.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueStages.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[5]'
      value: 'If you can find them and bring them back, ill let you borrow my ship. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueStages.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: I still need the parts
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueStages.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: The propellor blew away onto the island behind me. the bridge is in
        pieces. if you help me get it i can take you to the air temple
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueStages.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: The propellor blew away onto the island behind me. the bridge is in
        pieces. if you help me get it i can take you to the air temple
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueStages.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: You found the parts! I can fix the airship now.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueStages.Array.data[1].lockedLines.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 862432905181989318, guid: d021415f26a98114b8e25653e970283b, type: 3}
